==English==
===Etymology===
{{Rus.}}''step/e'' a grassy plain.
====Homophones====
*[[step]]
===Noun===
'''steppe''' ('''steppes''')
The name given the vast grass-plains of Eastern Europe and Asia. Similar to (US) [[prairie]] and (African) [[savannah]].
